    base:desc "The robot digital twin processes a continuous data stream from the physical robot. Real‑time requirements are emphasized; calculations must respect the control‑system dead time. Data are transmitted using MQTT, enabling near‑real‑time synchronization between physical measurements and the digital shadow. The system updates at the sensor sampling rate, providing low‑latency, continuous synchronization."
